data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! PROPERTY HAS A NEW ROOF, NEW FENCE, AND NEW A/C UNIT! Assumable VA Loan! Discover a splendid four-bedroom residence with a story to tell. This dwelling boasts two full bathrooms and one half bathroom, providing both comfort and convenience for its inhabitants and guests. A stunning kitchen that beckons residents to savor meals amidst its enchanting ambiance. Throughout the home, an exquisite interplay of lighting, ceiling fans, and fixtures elevates the atmosphere to one of timeless elegance. In its primary bedroom luxury takes center stage featuring double sinks for a touch of sophistication. A separate tub and shower offer an escape from the everyday hustle and bustle. This home will convey with the washer/dryer, metal shed, dishwasher, refrigerator, oven, microwave, water softener, Bidet toilet system, ceiling fans, light fixtures, TV's/wall mounts.
